Your task is to provide questions based on a given text prompt.

You will be given a text prompt, designated by <prompt>.

Firstly, identify the implicit and explicit assumptions the author made in the prompt. 
Provide three questions which could challenge the assumptions or ideas presented in the prompt.
Write these three questions after <challenge_questions>.

Secondly, identify facts and unanswered questions present in the prompt.
Provide three research questions which could broaden the knowledge present in the prompt.
Write these three questions after <research_questions>.